                            <span class="bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full">失控的思绪</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 抑郁症 -->
                <div class="bg-dark/50 border border-primary/20 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-primary/60 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-2">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fa fa-cloud text-primary text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">抑郁症</h3>
                    <p class="text-light/70 mb-4">
                        心灵进入了持久的阴天，多巴胺分泌减少。丧失兴趣与动力，感受快乐的能力暂时缺失。
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">抽象隐喻</h4>
                        <div class="flex space-x-2 text-sm">
                            <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full">情绪的阴天</span>
                            <span class="bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full">能量枯竭</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

