                        闯入性思维与强迫行为的循环。心灵被特定的念头和仪式困住，无法停止重复的动作或思考。
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">抽象隐喻</h4>
                        <div class="flex space-x-2 text-sm">
                            <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full">无限循环</span>
                            <span class="bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full">无法摆脱的脚本</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

